  patternId: pattern.3d-brawler-pawn-npc
  displayName: 3D Brawler Pawn And NPC
  description: A local 2-player 3D brawler route where player participants own rigged
    pawn bodies, a second player can join locally, and enemy or NPC actors can spawn
    into an arena for movement, attacks, animation, camera, and proof-readiness checks.
