  cautionaryCompanionPatterns: []
  setupNotes: "Create local player ParticipantDefinitions, assign PawnDefinitions
    with rigged 3D pawn prefabs, add input profiles for local join, place spawn points
    for each player, assign the shared camera rig and playfield profiles, add PlayerInputManager
    evidence only when local join is part of the proof, add enemy or NPC spawn evidence,
    then enter Play Mode after prefab, animator, movement, attack, and camera fields
    are assigned.\t"
